Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.35,0:24:30.12,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}又到了启程的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.35,0:24:37.40,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}叶间漏过点点阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.01,0:24:41.67,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}回想起一个个笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.06,0:24:49.01,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}还有曾经喧嚣的教室
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.33,0:24:54.65,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}轻轻迈开脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.89,0:24:59.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)\be1}去迎接一个新的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.28,0:25:02.12,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}那次邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.22,0:25:04.98,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}那晚倾心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.10,0:25:07.95,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}那些泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.05,0:25:11.22,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}都难以忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.30,0:25:18.05,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}小小的偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.27,0:25:22.68,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}成就了今日的我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.72,0:25:25.47,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}与你邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.58,0:25:28.45,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}与你相知
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.50,0:25:31.43,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}被你斥责
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.49,0:25:34.59,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}真是感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.69,0:25:41.54,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}让我们在十年后的今天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.74,0:25:46.02,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}怀着同样的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.14,0:25:51.19,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,600)\be1}再次相逢
