Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.47,0:00:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵 贵明同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小 小牧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.76,0:00:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.31,0:00:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不应该这么叫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过我们在这房间里独处时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要叫对方名字的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.58,0:00:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.13,0:00:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.24,0:00:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 爱佳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱佳？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.08,0:00:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是很难为情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.12,0:00:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.59,0:01:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你陪我做奇怪的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来要习惯和男生相处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还得花好多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 反正这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是说习惯就能习惯的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.22,0:01:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.26,0:01:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不讨厌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.50,0:01:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.09,0:01:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微有点难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.91,0:01:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但并不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边我来收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦贵明同学去收拾一下那边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.20,0:01:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道了 爱佳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵明…同学
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,// ----TEXT----
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵明同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小牧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人独处的时候要叫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱~佳~的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.51,0:03:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小牧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 小牧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是谁值日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.36,0:04:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己一个人在胡思乱想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 班长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说班长哎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂面和凉面有啥不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚纠结这问题以致深夜未眠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想班长说不定会知道答案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫我班长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长就是班长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.18,0:04:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了别叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 贵明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就叫小牧同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我的名字叫小牧爱佳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原来班长是叫爱佳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫 叫我小牧就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便当 便当
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 小牧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还能吃 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小牧同学你去书库吃午饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:05:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一会儿见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我觉得很过意不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 吃吧 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃 这个非常好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 用不着吃得那么急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你脸上沾着饭粒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.23,0:06:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙招待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我来喂你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛笑眯眯的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没笑眯眯的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说什么张嘴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.33,0:07:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是在妄想给谁喂便当啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能这样 爱佳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为道歉 就把我的便当给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 没事 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我去买个新的面包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:08:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对味道又没影响 而且这是雄二的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是向坂同学的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜拳输了 就被当跑腿的使唤了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说被女生坐过的面包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙反而会吃得津津有味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸上沾着饭粒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个绝对够大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看吗 要看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看要看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高处的书就让我来放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河野同学只是陪我练习而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小牧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 小牧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽 虽然瞥见了 但没在看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为惩罚 我要拿你做实验对象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验对象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是不可抗力的事故啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,申诉驳回
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好弄到些比较少见的茶叶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了点冰镇红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰镇红茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般的做法是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用开水泡出红茶倒入冰镇的容器中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果做的不好的话会变得很浑浊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我先把茶水滤出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰箱里放了一晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我也来一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的把我当实验对象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小牧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好凉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请拿去穿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不会留下什么污渍的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放这稍微晾一下就会干了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜 又让河野同学看到我丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是丢脸二连击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视上的星相占卜还说会有好事发生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱佳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本书放这个书架上没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 爱佳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可以 贵明同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵明同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.12,0:12:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还那么好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.23,0:12:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋 我没带伞哎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 河野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.83,0:12:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不靠过来一点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀就要淋湿了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再靠过来一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:13:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被别人看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 贵明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻站着干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了贵明 忘带伞了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人就该时刻都准备周全
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你伞靠过来点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别拉我伞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想这么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要淋湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我的伞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在妄想些奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱佳你要振作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕向坂同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:14:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家注意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个月的活动预定表都写在这上面了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要好好看一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.84,0:14:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小牧同学 我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 河野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.26,0:14:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 贵明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道当上副班长了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮一下忙的话就能快点做完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你们两个关系是不是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后两人单独在书库里久留不归
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.16,0:14:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 咻咻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了 只是在帮忙而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向坂同学你别说奇怪的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄二你也来帮忙捡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.83,0:14:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别拒绝得那么干脆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆 爽快的拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:15:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…刚才被大家取笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你指雄二说的那些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是口无遮拦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.11,0:15:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不该这么叫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当两人在这里独处的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 贵明同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把书打包好之后帮我泡杯茶吧 爱佳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今天还有非常好吃的茶点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵明同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说小牧同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在时候也不早了 不会有人在的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 也对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:15:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什么事 爱佳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:15:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是随便叫下你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说贵明同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊 雄二 真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天老姐似乎要派很多学生会的活给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我就一个人躲在校舍的角落里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避风头避到很晚才回家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 孤零零的我垂头丧气地走向校舍门口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在鞋箱附近看到了好事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱佳 和我一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 无论去哪我都会陪伴在贵明的左右
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你这是演的哪出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你和班长两人相互叫对方名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:17:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵明同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱佳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你们两个有问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 快招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.77,0:17:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在帮忙整理书库而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那用得着相互叫名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是练习而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥 什么练习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习就是 就是练习啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.90,0:17:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神魂颠倒 得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚是姐姐你最喜欢吃的炸虾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:18:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不来的话 我就都吃掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河野贵明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 由真
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你直呼爱佳的名字 却不直呼我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.71,0:18:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 由真
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 由真？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你别以为你这么就算赢了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小贵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 笹森同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须叫我花梨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话我就公开那个录像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珊瑚 小琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫珊瑚和琉璃就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我可不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么只要直呼我的名字就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 小珊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久寿川学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连久寿川学姐也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 草壁同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.05,0:19:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 露子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小贵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不叫我环啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 阿贵 木实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木实的话不是一直都叫木实的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕木实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环 环
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.65,0:20:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然老姐还是比较适合称呼后面加个大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裂了 裂了 要裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来晚了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被雄二缠上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 今天这就结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 河野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想中止练习
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.51,0:21:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 河野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想今后你还是不要再来这里比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小牧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 加我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河 河野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又忘记带伞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.46,0:21:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…要是被别人看到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好无情 让我淋雨回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是那意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:21:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样又会给河野同学添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了我不在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 我今天还特意跑去书库
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却吃了小牧同学的闭门羹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.06,0:22:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 还是快回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.55,0:22:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.12,0:22:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 最近雨真是频繁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要注意不能忘记带伞了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.12,0:22:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是真的不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被别人看到的话 又要被八卦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.65,0:22:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小牧同学讨厌和我一起被八卦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.45,0:22:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒没…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.52,0:22:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不靠过来一点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀要淋湿了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.06,0:22:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.90,0:22:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.52,0:22:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的被别人看见的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小牧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.89,0:22:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小牧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨已经停了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.61,0:23:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.01,0:23:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 这不就是小牧同学的家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我怎么又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.98,0:23:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.31,0:23:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.77,0:23:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.52,0:23:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有劳你帮我打伞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.95,0:23:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.43,0:23:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.60,0:23:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话 要不要来我家喝杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.82,0:23:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵明同学
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.92,0:23:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.53,0:23:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱佳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.94,0:23:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁乃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.37,0:23:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 这不是河野贵明吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.84,0:23:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是成电灯泡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.18,0:23:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 郁乃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,// ----NEXT----
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.75,0:26:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.15,0:26:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西露法妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.18,0:26:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈露美妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.15,0:26:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依露法小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.86,0:26:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把妹妹两个字去掉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.77,0:26:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我哈~露~美~
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.89,0:26:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还叫人家小姐 真见外
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.76,0:26:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你们三位…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.12,0:26:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人应该把女仆机器人当仆人般直呼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.71,0:26:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将来要成为达令的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.83,0:26:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理应叫我哈露美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.43,0:26:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能叫我依露法的话我会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.41,0:26:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你们在忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.00,0:26:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春夏阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.63,0:26:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贵
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.70,0:27:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我春~夏~就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.76,0:27:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连春夏阿姨也
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.33,0:27:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和阿贵谁跟谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.11,0:27:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是刚刚认识
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.66,0:27:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请恕我直言
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.23,0:27:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这不是相处时日长短的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.23,0:27:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.46,0:27:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令的爱才是最关键的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.75,0:27:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在阿贵还是婴儿的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.39,0:27:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还经常帮他换尿布啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.49,0:27:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尿布
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.38,0:27:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候阿贵的○○还是那样小巧玲珑 太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.07,0:27:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很 很小巧玲珑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.68,0:27:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上幼儿园的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.43,0:27:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路后会很寂寞地在我的胸口○○的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.26,0:27:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真 真羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.75,0:27:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还经常一起洗澡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.70,0:28:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贵那时候真是的 总是○○还会○○
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.88,0:28:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我可从来都没…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.91,0:28:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.80,0:28:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的阿贵 连大人都要甘拜下风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.92,0:28:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是早熟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.14,0:28:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甘 甘拜下风
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.66,0:28:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀


